<h2>6. Our Financial Aid Blog is Overseen by Educational Experts</h2>
<p>We have relationships with  educational consultants, financial aid directors/officers, and others who work daily on a face-to-face basis with college students and their financial issues. All of our up-to-date news, opinion, and commentary concerning financial aid and other college-related topics can be accessed by subscribing and <a href="https://www.collegescholarships.org/blog/">reading our Financial Aid Blog</a>.</p>




